#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1240099200.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "The first bugfix-release of xfce 4.6 has been released.\n"
msgstr "Выпущен первый корректирующий выпуск Xfce 4.6.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1240099200.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thanks to all the people who have been using xfce 4.6 and took the time and effort to submit bugreports for stuff that wasn't quite working the way it is supposed to. We have been able to fix several issues during the past few weeks.\n"
